☁️ AWS (Amazon Web Services)
Provided by Amazon Web Services
Launched in 2006 (oldest cloud provider)
Most widely used cloud platform 🌍
..............📌 Services............
EC2 → Virtual servers
S3 → Storage
RDS → Databases
Lambda → Serverless computing
................🚀 Features...............
Very large number of services
High scalability & reliability
Global data centers (regions & availability zones)
................👍 Best For..............
Startups and enterprises
Projects needing many service options
.......🌟 Real-Time Examples.........
Netflix uses AWS for streaming 🎬
Many startups host apps on AWS
